      </processinfo>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_52370a1a1432dee30002a4db40315341">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Amiri Baraka Papers contains poetry, pamphlet publications, scripts, interviews, photographs, correspondence, and posters of work written or edited by Amiri Baraka, both under the name Amiri Baraka as well as LeRoi Jones. This material mostly documents his professional work between 1965 and 1982 and reflects his work as a playwright and poet.</p>
      </scopecontent>
